GENERALCOMMENTS:
i think text-based and GUI should be combined from the beginning so that a user can switch whenever wanted. drag and drop can be very useful. also for adjusting the order, drag and drop can be very handy if only slight changes are needed. for a completely different order, the text-based approach is more handy.

for setting the video URL and title etc. i think that the text-based approach is more efficient. it is also easier to see mistakes and adjust them. thus, making the tete-based approach also more effective for this.

if everything needs to be done with the text-based approach, I am not sure if it will lead to a lot of mistakes (e.g., missing something) if done for a lot of videos. but using code excerpts as templates for a lot of modules could be very useful. (both for efficiency and effectiveness)
